            "title": "美股道指跌轉升　納指曾升1.55%　亞馬遜急升近10%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美股3大指數扭轉上日弱勢，10月累計連升6至7個月。聯儲局多名委員反對本周及12月減息，言論限制大市單日升幅。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240801_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240801_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">美股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">道瓊斯工業平均指數表現反覆，收報47562點，升40點，升幅約0.1%。高開137點後，反覆曾挫174點，其後一度倒升196點見47671點。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240801_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240801_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">美股 (AP圖片)</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/04/Earns_Amazon_25072517689079.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/04/Earns_Amazon_25072517689079.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"微軟 Microsoft (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20240731_FI_source-ap_Earns_Microsoft_24211762243142.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"微軟 Microsoft (AP圖片)\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20240731_FI_source-ap_Earns_Microsoft_24211762243142.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">微軟 Microsoft (AP圖片)</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/724x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/bplib_20250224-182216_20250224_Netflix_source-web.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/724x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/bplib_20250224-182216_20250224_Netflix_source-web.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240801_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">美股 (AP圖片)</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/04/Earns_Amazon_25072517689079.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"微軟 Microsoft (AP圖片)\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20240731_FI_source-ap_Earns_Microsoft_24211762243142.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">微軟 Microsoft (AP圖片)</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/724x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/bplib_20250224-182216_20250224_Netflix_source-web.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">標普500指數報6840點，升17點，升幅約0.3%，一度漲0.83%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">納斯達克指數報23724點，升143點，升幅逾0.6%，最多反彈365點或1.55%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">反映中國概念股表現的金龍指數反彈0.53%，報8273點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">10月累計，Alphabet漲15.7%，連續上漲7個月，亞馬遜升11.2%，英偉達彈8.5%，延續此前一個月上揚7.1%的表現。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">3大指數全星期累計都連升3星期，本周累計，道指上揚0.8%，標指進賬0.7%，納指攀升2.2%，金龍指數則回吐1.1%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">10月累計，道指走高2.5%，為自2018年以來首次錄得連升6個月；標指抽高2.3%，納指急彈4.7%，金龍指數則滑落4.2%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/04/Earns_Amazon_25072517689079.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/04/Earns_Amazon_25072517689079.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">亞馬遜上季雲計算業務好過預期，股價曾大升12.4%，升穿250美元創新高，收市升9.6%，支撐大市表現，市值進賬近3000億美元，收市仍升9.6%，為漲幅最大道指成份股。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">其餘科技股個別發展，微軟回吐1.5%，為表現最差道指成份股 ; 蘋果公司唱好今季業務前景，股價漲2.2%後倒跌0.4%收市，Meta跌2.72%，Tesla升3.74%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"微軟 Microsoft (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20240731_FI_source-ap_Earns_Microsoft_24211762243142.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"微軟 Microsoft (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20240731_FI_source-ap_Earns_Microsoft_24211762243142.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">微軟 Microsoft (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">Netflix宣布1拆10股，另外據報集團正積極考慮收購華納兄弟探索，Netflix升2.7%，華納兄弟探索升3.84%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國第二大油企雪佛龍業績好過預期，股價上揚2.7%，加密貨幣交易所Coinbase上季收入勝預期，股價抽升4.7%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/724x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/bplib_20250224-182216_20250224_Netflix_source-web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/724x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/bplib_20250224-182216_20250224_Netflix_source-web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
